snippet.title: Rocket League Season 6 Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience the magic in this must-watch Rocket League Season 6 premiere trailer. 
Learn More: https://www.rocketleague.com/news/rocket-league-gets-animated-in-season-6/

Rocket League Season 6 starts on March 9, 2022. Prepare to get animated because Season 6 features the channel-surfing, road-tripping Nomad Van! Unlock fluffy and mysterious Nomster Items as you dive into the Season 6 Rocket Pass, and compete for all-new tournament rewards like the Dumbbell Topper and TP Goal Explosion.

#RocketLeague #RocketLeagueSeason6 #RocketPass
